<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-30-1180 </DOCNO><TEXT>The new laws on water management will pose more rigid requirements onleachate purification. A plant meeting these requirements is being operatedat the Heisterholz refuse tip. The plant comprises a biological purificationstage and a chemical/physical purification stage connected downstream.Purification efficiencies are discussed in detail. BSB/sub 5/ was reducedto 7 mg/l or by 98%.</TEXT></DOC>